            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="12421942">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">一旦地狱建成法治，下不下地狱便无所谓了。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-04-18 18:46</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>一旦地狱建成法治，下不下地狱便无所谓了。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

